---
title: Mexican Spiced Cauliflower with Charred Corn & Black Bean Slaw & Feta
description: Add Mexican flavours (don’t forget to adjust your spice level to suit!) to roasted cauliflower and you’ll transform this classic vegetable into a flavour sensation! This colourful bowl is creamy, rich and crunchy – just like the best salads should be.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5c5125c7e3f3396515312e42-31b901b9.jpg
